Description:
Near the road, you find some abandoned crates with a crest painted on one side that looks familiar.

It resembles the crest you found in Senenthia, but it is not an exact match. Unfortunately, the symbols on the crates are too damaged to confirm any details.

You are certain that these crates were abandoned long ago by their owners, and the locals have grown so accustomed to them that they now see them as part of the scenery. Perhaps they hold answers to the mystery of your crest, or perhaps searching them will simply be a waste of time.
DescriptionAction: It is up to your group to decide what to do next.
